\par\pard\plain \fi360\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Well. To begin with, I don\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92t know how I did or when it first started. Because I didn\u8217\'92t realize it when it happened. But, somehow or another, I got the feeling that I would have a better time with younger people. Which I was havin a pretty good time. Until I realized it all had to come to an end. The way I realized that was to get a divorce. I don\u8217\'92think I could be married to a man like him.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Why is that?}
